data.description: Is it time for a new front porch to sip your coffee on? I have just the one for you with a peaceful view! This beautiful 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home is move in ready and sits on 7 acres! The semi open floor plan makes for a spacious feel and the kitchen isn't lacking in cabinet or counter space- a cook's delight! Hard floors throughout make cleaning a breeze! Additional perks include an automatic generator, a storm shelter, and covered parking is already in place for your camper/RV! Properties with acreage in AR are in high demand so don't delay in scheduling your look!
